zReview-Commit-ID: Clmu6iRCG20", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/apz_test_utils.js", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/helper_hittest_touchaction.html", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/test_group_hittest.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fce6b794a239a5341e6b8da4bd53a970626e1120", "parents": ["4432fb67de2d1e2658a36fed800979c1968c1f94"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Wander Lairson Costa \u003cwcosta@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1465505: Replace PRMJ_Now() by mozilla::TimeStamp r=jonco\n\nNotice as TimeStamp is not an integral type, it can't be wrapped by\nmozilla::Atomic. There two uses of it, which seems to not harm the code,\nbut I am not entirily sure.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 3A1HL3L3tkW", "files": ["js/public/SliceBudget.h", "js/src/gc/GC.cpp", "js/src/gc/GCRuntime.h", "js/src/gc/Scheduling.h", "js/src/gc/SliceBudget.cpp", "js/src/jsfriendapi.cpp", "js/src/moz.build", "js/src/vm/Realm.h", "js/src/vm/Runtime.cpp", "js/src/vm/Runtime.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c115f0bb2bfbfc808f7a09a03f808aa80aeabfde", "parents": ["fce6b794a239a5341e6b8da4bd53a970626e1120"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brindusan Cristian \u003ccbrindusan@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset c115f0bb2bfb (bug 1465505) spidermonkey bustages. CLOSED TREE", "files": ["js/public/SliceBudget.h", "js/src/gc/GC.cpp", "js/src/gc/GCRuntime.h", "js/src/gc/Scheduling.h", "js/src/gc/SliceBudget.cpp", "js/src/jsfriendapi.cpp", "js/src/moz.build", "js/src/vm/Realm.h", "js/src/vm/Runtime.cpp", "js/src/vm/Runtime.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ef06853a18a59002945d9ebb29944296f9da2dcc", "parents": ["c115f0bb2bfbfc808f7a09a03f808aa80aeabfde"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Hiroyuki Ikezoe \u003chikezoe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1468124 - Don't calculate overflow area if there is any frames in preserve-3d context. r=mattwoodrow\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 2Ts3MzdouB7", "files": ["layout/painting/RetainedDisplayListBuilder.cpp", "layout/painting/crashtests/1468124-1.html", "layout/painting/crashtests/crashtests.list"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "245c6fe9938cd895ea56194c34d0bde72bfd995d", "parents": ["ef06853a18a59002945d9ebb29944296f9da2dcc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Makoto Kato \u003cm_kato@ga2.so-net.ne.jp\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1421510 - Part 1. Make nsITextServicesFilter builtinclass. r=masayuki\n\nThere is no JavaScript implementation (including c-c and bluegriffon) for\nnsITextServicesFilter, so we make this builtin to access builtin C++\nimplementation directly.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: BGZlDzsKT6N", "files": ["editor/spellchecker/nsITextServicesFilter.idl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9941588e63261810b56446113d8fe9c07116b185", "parents": ["245c6fe9938cd895ea56194c34d0bde72bfd995d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Makoto Kato \u003cm_kato@ga2.so-net.ne.jp\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1421510 - Part 2. Use nsComposeTxtSrvFilter directly. r=masayuki\n\nnsITextServicesFilter is builtin class, so we can store nsComposeTxtSrvFilter\ninstead of nsITextServicesFilter.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: ErZQwWC0Wjx", "files": ["editor/spellchecker/EditorSpellCheck.cpp", "editor/spellchecker/EditorSpellCheck.h", "editor/spellchecker/TextServicesDocument.cpp", "editor/spellchecker/TextServicesDocument.h", "editor/spellchecker/nsFilteredContentIterator.cpp", "editor/spellchecker/nsFilteredContentIterator.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9afd36a4db260d2ed08b2526aa7a659a78737409", "parents": ["9941588e63261810b56446113d8fe9c07116b185"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Makoto Kato \u003cm_kato@ga2.so-net.ne.jp\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1421510 - Part 3. Make nsITextServicesFilter.skip noscript access. r=masayuki\n\nnsITextServicesFilter.skip isn't accessed from JavaScript (including c-c and\nbluegriffon), so we can remove it from IDL.\n\nAlso, skip method should use early return style for clean up.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: qjZS54ZeoT", "files": ["editor/spellchecker/nsComposeTxtSrvFilter.cpp", "editor/spellchecker/nsComposeTxtSrvFilter.h", "editor/spellchecker/nsFilteredContentIterator.cpp", "editor/spellchecker/nsITextServicesFilter.idl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9222fabb7ee60a94d923094afb6867d4fd05d4bb", "parents": ["9afd36a4db260d2ed08b2526aa7a659a78737409"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Gurzau Raul \u003crgurzau@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge mozilla-central to autoland. a=merge CLOSED TREE", "files": ["js/src/jsfriendapi.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "d1d36d462a35b2023f4f9e181749fae1da2391bc", "parents": ["9222fabb7ee60a94d923094afb6867d4fd05d4bb", "257c191e7903523a1132e04460a0b2460d950809"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Valentin Gosu \u003cvalentin.gosu@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1426019 - Use nsIThread in nsHostResolver r=bagder\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: LOt7VX9mj7r", "files": ["netwerk/dns/nsHostResolver.cpp", "netwerk/dns/nsHostResolver.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "80dd9e57c3a4544ea7c8284efec3f2f6e6e4d1c2", "parents": ["d1d36d462a35b2023f4f9e181749fae1da2391bc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Banner \u003cstandard8@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1230193 - Finish enabling ESLint rule no-undef for devtools/. r=jdescottes\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: EVFivqFNy8a", "files": ["devtools/.eslintrc.js", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/.eslintrc.js", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/Debugger.Source.prototype.element.js", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_connectToFrame.html", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_css-logic-media-queries.html", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_getProcess.html", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_inspector-pseudoclass-lock.html", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_webextension-addon-debugging-connect.html"], "git_node": nul