 \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1459696 - Respect nested inactive layer clips when combining a layer's event regions into its ancestors'. r=mstange\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: GkGSOeDvkvS", "files": ["layout/painting/FrameLayerBuilder.cpp", "layout/painting/FrameLayerBuilder.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c4312c1591dd786be51286a198d6cb4e92381022", "parents": ["035c6c98707309ffb94e5814c1b62588a6171889"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1459696 - Add a mochitest. r=kats\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: JHx89SwL4xG", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/helper_hittest_nested_transforms_bug1459696.html", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/test_group_hittest.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cd61f8689a52abce352384fac7528ced82e4c656", "parents": ["c4312c1591dd786be51286a198d6cb4e92381022"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1459696 - Remove an unused overload of SetTargetAPZC(). r=kats\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: HiQKx5Ickcd", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/src/APZCTreeManager.cpp", "gfx/layers/apz/src/APZCTreeManager.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c8a9cee249aa5a5b849de10870b2ef2daaab352b", "parents": ["cd61f8689a52abce352384fac7528ced82e4c656"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Robin Templeton \u003crobin@igalia.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1441098 - Part 1: Add BigInt support in BufferGrayRootsTracer. r=sfink\n\nThis class is used for tracing DOM objects.", "files": ["js/src/gc/RootMarking.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f87f53656ed51696c9b00b794f8718313f7e2721", "parents": ["c8a9cee249aa5a5b849de10870b2ef2daaab352b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Robin Templeton \u003crobin@igalia.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1441098 - Part 2: Define BigInt serialization methods. r=sfink\n\nwriteBytes serializes a BigInt value as a little-endian byte sequence,\nignoring its sign. createFromBytes can be used to deserialize the output\nof writeBytes.", "files": ["js/src/vm/BigIntType.cpp", "js/src/vm/BigIntType.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "940e6648c1f24868b5017f8fd4ed5b9a105bb848", "parents": ["f87f53656ed51696c9b00b794f8718313f7e2721"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Robin Templeton \u003crobin@igalia.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1441098 - Part 3: Add structured clone support for BigInt. r=sfink\n\nNew data types are defined for primitive BigInt values and BigInt\nobjects. BigInts are serialized starting with 32 bits of sign and length\ninformation, followed by a little-endian byte sequence representing an\nunsigned integer.", "files": ["js/src/vm/StructuredClone.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "84ae27690d6b756b64d9bb951db4a035e7e56102", "parents": ["940e6648c1f24868b5017f8fd4ed5b9a105bb848"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Robin Templeton \u003crobin@igalia.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1441098 - Part 4: Enable BigInt wrapping from DOM bindings. r=bz", "files": ["dom/bindings/BindingUtils.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a41bcbc841f9baf2eaf67f4c166331e618d21b66", "parents": ["84ae27690d6b756b64d9bb951db4a035e7e56102"], "tags": []}, {"author": "arthur.iakab \u003caiakab@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset 7f4c085cf228 (bug 1443505) for failing Gtests on Assertion failure TelemetryScalar.cpp:773", "files": ["toolkit/components/telemetry/tests/gtest/TestScalars.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f6e0c19170833b17111a042e9a1fe89d4d97dbdc", "parents": ["a41bcbc841f9baf2eaf67f4c166331e618d21b66"], "tags": []}, {"author": "sotaro \u003csotaro.ikeda.g@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1469791 - Use longer timeout for AcquireSync() r=nical", "files": ["gfx/webrender_bindings/RenderD3D11TextureHostOGL.cpp"], "git_node": 