 Hengst \u003carchaeopteryx@coole-files.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1480517 - Unregister remote service DBus object at nsDBusRemoteService::Shutdown(). r=jhorak, a=RyanVM", "files": ["toolkit/components/remote/nsDBusRemoteService.cpp", "toolkit/components/remote/nsDBusRemoteService.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b402d46ca93bf5385731c4cea666496cf806695a", "parents": ["7701b607a4550c8afce39bea2bebe2682b6069fc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Justin Wood \u003cCallek@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1463749 - Support checksum .beet files having duplicate content, as long as sha's match. r=mtabara, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D2756", "files": ["testing/mozharness/scripts/release/generate-checksums.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b93cd3e23a6c6d26719c88d881527ae0348c34a5", "parents": ["b402d46ca93bf5385731c4cea666496cf806695a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Justin Wood \u003cCallek@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1463749 - Langpack Checksums. r=mtabara, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D2446", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/config.yml", "taskcluster/ci/post-beetmover-checksums-dummy/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-beetmover-signed-langpacks-checksums/kind.yml", "taskcluster/docs/kinds.rst", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/beetmover_langpack_checksums.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "af8e3fb57cb74c9acb0d28123ef2268f42951751", "parents": ["b93cd3e23a6c6d26719c88d881527ae0348c34a5"], "tags": []}], "date": 1533916004, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9637": {"changesets": [{"author": "Csoregi Natalia \u003cncsoregi@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out 2 changesets (bug 1477817) for build bustage on WebGLExtensionMOZDebug.cpp. a=backout\n\nBacked out changeset 7701b607a455 (bug 1477817)\nBacked out changeset 8e8f202579a1 (bug 1477817)", "files": ["dom/canvas/WebGLContext.h", "dom/canvas/WebGLExtensionMOZDebug.cpp", "dom/canvas/test/webgl-mochitest/mochitest.ini", "dom/canvas/test/webgl-mochitest/test_has_rbab.html", "dom/webidl/WebGLRenderingContext.webidl", "gfx/gl/GLContextProviderEGL.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "823e87ee74753871c887babc22282a5b6760b1bd", "parents": ["af8e3fb57cb74c9acb0d28123ef2268f42951751"], "tags": []}], "date": 1533923099, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ncsoregi@mozilla.com"}, "9638": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nit -\u003e a1d82b8c55fb\nkab -\u003e 935b8215653b", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7d7f2612ca513f26ae38726661bbc53d63a131a1", "parents": ["823e87ee74753871c887babc22282a5b6760b1bd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nda -\u003e ed3098bf2f0e\nhu -\u003e a61726d8488b\nnb-NO -\u003e 7d02ed5b5b25\nnn-NO -\u003e 51c735d86669\nru -\u003e aec9c1e5f16b", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d645f9af7e169920167a298f6654b123f62e6730", "parents": ["7d7f2612ca513f26ae38726661bbc53d63a131a1"], "tags": []}], "date": 1533924035, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "9639": {"changesets": [{"author": "Kris Maglione \u003cmaglione.k@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1470965 - Fix refcount sanity in nsIPrincipal.addonPolicy getter. r=mixedpuppy, a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: KuDN3joKi7S", "files": ["caps/BasePrincipal.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "adfbbc7a8f60df66e65681878875e8680cfe3d41", "parents": ["d645f9af7e169920167a298f6654b123f62e6730"], "tags": []}, {"author": "James Teh \u003cjteh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1471466 - Don't fire a focus event for a remote accessible if focus has moved into the chrome since the event was sent. r=surkov, a=lizzard\n\nFor example, this can happen when choosing File menu -\u003e new Tab.\nFocus briefly returns to the document in the original tab, so we ask that document to restore focus.\nThe remote document then sends a focus event to the parent.\nHowever, before the parent can process that event, focus has already moved to the address bar for the new tab.\nWith this check, we discover that focus is now in the chrome and thus avoid firing the event for the remote accessible.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 7k58dzREqZD", "files": ["accessible/windows/msaa/Platform.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3a49b45d34288c6b6cebb18971fa7be93a4a21d7", "parents": ["adfbbc7a8f60df66e65681878875e8680cfe3d41"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Christoph Kerschbaumer \u003cckerschb@christophkerschbaumer.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1475073 - Pass individual CORS errors as categories to web console error messages. r=baku, a=lizzard", "files": ["dom/base/test/test_warning_for_blocked_cross_site_request.html", "netwerk/protocol/http/HttpChannelChild.cpp", "netwerk/protocol/http/HttpChannelChild.h", "netwerk/protocol/http/HttpChannelParent.cpp", "netwerk/protocol/http/HttpChannelParent.h", "netwerk/protocol/http/InterceptedHttpChannel.cpp", "netwerk/protocol/http/InterceptedHttpChannel.h", "netwerk/protocol/http/NullHttpChannel.cpp", "netwerk/protocol/http/PHttpChannel.ipdl", "netwerk/protocol/http/nsCORSListenerProxy.cpp", "netwerk/protocol/http/nsCORSListenerProxy.h", "netwerk/protocol/http/nsHttpChannel.cpp", "netwerk/protocol/http/nsHttpChannel.h", "netwerk/protocol/http/nsIHttpChannel.idl", "netwerk/protocol/viewsource/nsViewSourceChannel.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null]