 - Dynamically show hidden audio tabs in all tabs menu r=dao a=lizzard\n\nWhen a hidden audio tab is muted it isn't pulled into the main all tabs\npanel. Unmuting that tab will now add it to the main all tabs panel,\neven if the all tabs menu it open.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 2HtZvy7aBsG", "files": ["browser/modules/TabsList.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "37110fa0b0b1e45da7b64065ffb260a992a5d218", "parents": ["dd14588873be5a53f2666aad499575a82fd08d54"], "tags": []}], "date": 1534662788, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "rgurzau@mozilla.com"}, "9686": {"changesets": [{"author": "Matt Howell \u003cmhowell@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1481907 Part 1 - Block updater code from using paths containing invalid symlinks. r=rstrong a=lizzard", "files": ["toolkit/mozapps/update/common/updatecommon.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7138f70c03dd460311a5703ea22004d500481fab", "parents": ["37110fa0b0b1e45da7b64065ffb260a992a5d218"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matt Howell \u003cmhowell@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1481907 Part 2 - Remove uses of GetTempFileName from updater code. r=rstrong a=lizzard", "files": ["toolkit/mozapps/update/common/moz.build", "toolkit/mozapps/update/common/updatecommon.cpp", "toolkit/mozapps/update/common/updatehelper.cpp", "toolkit/mozapps/update/common/updatehelper.h", "toolkit/mozapps/update/updater/updater.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f87d4e897762e2bbb64f91afd9cc9f07af4f1c13", "parents": ["7138f70c03dd460311a5703ea22004d500481fab"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matt Howell \u003cmhowell@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1481907 followup - Fix a memory allocation oversight. r=me a=lizzard", "files": ["toolkit/mozapps/update/common/updatecommon.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fdc1b7954e76e316c9c64550c0107680dc429e48", "parents": ["f87d4e897762e2bbb64f91a